    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 home-page-text">
      <p>Nest-Eggy is a one stop shop for aggregating all of your bank account information in one place. We then give you invaluable advice to help you grow your net worth.</p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="row text-image-pair">
