      <p>We track your weekly spending accross all your accounts and offer you valuable feedback and expertise on specific areas you can target to reduce your expenses.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 front-page-picto"><i class="fa fa-pie-chart" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row text-image-pair home-page-text">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 front-page-picto"><i class="fa fa-table" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
      <p>You can also find the details of every payments you've made and received in the transaction history tab.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>




